<br>
First off, SoS is NOT way too slow for primary. We've had that beat into our heads for a very long time, but it's simply not true.<br>
<br>
SoS is better in mainhand stat-wise until 60, when the damage bonus for jade mace finally catches up to the superior ratio of the SoS. However, the SoS is SO good in offhand, that even though it's a better mainhand weapon, the best combo of Jade Mace and SoS is to have JM in mainhand.<br>
<br>
I have always been a proponent of SoS/SoS. On my server, they are roughly similar in cost, equally available, and dual SoS is far superior to JM/SoS until the highest of levels.<br>
<br>
As an example, here are the comparative modal numbers at level 40<br>
SoS main/JM   off :  2.123<br>
JM   main/SoS off :  2.164<br>
SoS main/SoS off :  2.279<br>
<br>
Hope that made some sense <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->   <p></p><i>Edited by: <A HREF=http://pub35.ezboard.com/ueleyrin.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Eleyrin</A> at: 9/3/02 5:11:30 pm<br></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#cccccc><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub35.ezboard.com/udamaniel71.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Damaniel71</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Monk</span><br>  Posts: 140<br> <font color=#8b1a1a>(9/6/02 11:08:41 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fmonklybusiness43508frm6.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=1850.topic&index=3>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: JM/SoS combo question</span><hr size=1> All ya gotta do is take a graphics calculator and make two equations, and here is the setup:<br>
<br>
Y= (weapon damage + X)  /  (weapon delay)<br>
X= your level's damage bonus<br>
<br>
So, a jade mace would be as follows...<br>
<br>
Y= (9 + X)  /  18<br>
<br>
and the SoS,<br>
<br>
Y= (17 + X)  /  27<br>
<br>
You will find that the jade mace will become equal to the SoS with a 7 primary hand damage bonus. Thus, at level 49 the jade mace will become better in primary hand. At 46 they will become equal, and before then the SoS is a better primary hand. Procs more too. <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> <br>
<br>
